      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TURTLE TIME (1) stuck on well last time to finish 1.5 lengths back in second (22.93) at Warragul in a Grade 5 over 400m. Likely to feature again. LUCA SKYWALKER (4) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Hay Riley (25.05) in a Grade 5 H. Got back and turned spotting a start but found the line impressively. Will give a great sight again. DAINTREE VISION (3) produced a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 435m behind Oddly Cool (25.08) in a Grade 5 H. Has performed well from this box with a win and eight minor placings to his name from 15 starts. Key player if finds best. SNITCH ADAMS (7) scored last time and appeals as a top-three prospect.",
